### Our board API (search + detail). Anonymous. Pick the `local` environment
# (status bar) and run `next dev`. Seed data first: npx tsx scripts/seed.ts (CR-8).

@json = Content-Type: application/json

### Search — no filters (whole board, page 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clans/search
{{json}}

{ "page": 1, "pageSize": 8 }

### Search — by playstyle tags (OR within)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clans/search
{{json}}

{ "tags": ["PvE", "Raids"], "page": 1, "pageSize": 8 }

### Search — combined filters (AND across categories)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clans/search
{{json}}

{ "languages": ["Russian"], "regions": ["EUROPE"], "membershipTypes": ["OPEN"], "page": 1, "pageSize": 8 }

### Search — by name (case-insensitive substring)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clans/search
{{json}}

{ "name": "wolf", "page": 1, "pageSize": 8 }

### Search — member-count range
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clans/search
{{json}}

{ "minMembers": 20, "maxMembers": 50, "page": 1, "pageSize": 8 }

### Search — page 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clans/search
{{json}}

{ "page": 2, "pageSize": 8 }

### Search — invalid (pageSize > 50 → 400 INVALID_REQUEST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/clans/search
{{json}}

{ "page": 1, "pageSize": 99 }
